    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "STEP 1 \u2014 TRIGGER\n\nRuns automatically every Monday at 9:00 AM via cron schedule. No manual action needed. Initiates the full pipeline.",
        "height": 140,
        "color": 7
      },
      "id": "b4edd6ad-2fca-4a54-bf32-c6d521bbcdbd",
      "name": "Note 1",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -4736,
        3776
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "STEP 2 \u2014 DISCOVERY\n\nApify Instagram Hashtag Scraper is triggered via HTTP POST. Hashtags: #fitnessindia #indianfitness #fitnessmotivation.\n\nA 45-second wait allows the scraper to complete. Results are then fetched via HTTP GET.\n\nOutput: Raw profile JSON data.",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 420,
        "color": 3
      },
      "id": "fc347cde-d006-42e4-9aa9-d8bf18279af6",
      "name": "Note 2",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -4416,
        3648
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "STEP 3 \u2014 FILTERING\n\nOnly profiles with 5,000 to 100,000 followers pass through. Profiles outside this range are dropped automatically.",
        "height": 140,
        "width": 260,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "cbc7b753-c3f1-4c62-bfde-98058c154f48",
      "name": "Note 3",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -2992,
        3776
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "STEP 4 \u2014 ENRICHMENT\n\nFor each profile:\n- Engagement Rate calculated from avg likes and comments\n- Email extracted from bio via regex\n- City detected from bio text\n- Content themes classified from bio keywords\n\nAll 13 sheet columns are populated here.",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 300,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "f3e83278-ac15-46be-9ef8-5095fa7a8fa8",
      "name": "Note 4",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -2688,
        3728
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "STEP 5 \u2014 SEGMENTATION\n\nSegment A \u2014 Nano Creators\n<=30K followers and >=4% engagement\nCollab type: Barter / UGC\n\nSegment B \u2014 Mid Tier Micro\n30K-100K followers and >=2% engagement\nCollab type: Paid Sponsorship / Affiliate\n\nSegment C \u2014 High Potential\n>=5% engagement regardless of follower count\nCollab type: Brand Ambassador\n\nAll three are merged and the segment label is stored in the Segment column of the sheet. Use filter view in Google Sheets to view each segment separately.",
        "height": 300,
        "width": 360,
        "color": 6
      },
      "id": "4f61b95f-94f6-42d7-ac7a-1f1b9a78898b",
      "name": "Note 5",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -2384,
        3408
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "STEP 6 \u2014 AI MESSAGE GENERATION\n\nEach influencer is processed one at a time via a loop.\n\nGemini 1.5 Flash generates:\n1. Email Pitch (60-90 words) \u2014 professional, references niche, themes, collaboration type\n2. Instagram DM (15-30 words) \u2014 casual and direct\n\nA 60-second wait between iterations prevents Gemini API rate limit errors.\n\nResponse is parsed from JSON and attached to the record.",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 360,
        "color": 2
      },
      "id": "b473bf8b-df67-4ecb-9c00-0088c9a79ded",
      "name": "Note 6",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1856,
        3680
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "STEP 7 \u2014 DATA STORAGE\n\nAll 13 fields written to the Raw Data tab in Google Sheets.\n\nTo view by segment, use the filter view on the Segment column. No separate tabs needed \u2014 everything is in one clean sheet.",
        "height": 180,
        "width": 300
      },
      "id": "c5669410-6e4b-4eca-8e6c-850eb2ace6ec",
      "name": "Note 7",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1104,
        3696
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "STEP 8 \u2014 OUTREACH\n\nIf email found in bio: Gmail node sends outreach automatically. Sheet is updated to Sent.\n\nIf no email found: Row is saved in sheet. DM message is ready for manual sending via Instagram or tools like ManyChat.\n\nNote: Meta Graph API requires business approval for automated DM sending.",
        "height": 220,
        "width": 340,
        "color": 3
      },
      "id": "e1764721-9ac6-42a3-bec1-d37b2e420fb2",
      "name": "Note 8",
